headline: Candace Vickery, Kimberly Rose
abstract: The couple met at a brunch with friends in Asheville, N.C., in 2018, and had their first date soon afterward.
lead_paragraph: Candace Michael Vickery and Kimberly Vel Rose were married Dec. 31 in Greenville, S.C. Vivian L. Hunnings, who was ordained through American Marriage Ministries, officiated at the Hilton Greenville hotel.
